      <h2 style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">Main Goal</h2>
      <p>
        Detect all relevant objects in as many images as possible of a common
        test set from the ImageNet object detection data set within 10 minutes.
      </p>
      <p>&nbsp;</p>
      <h2 style="border-bottom: 1px dotted;">Scoring System</h2>
      <p>
        Final score is the image processing score divided by the energy
        consumption.
      </p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <img
